RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 1 6F Dirt CR: 29. Maiden Claiming Purse 10340. FOR NATIVE MAIDENS, FILLIES TWO YEARS OLD. Weight, 116 lbs. Claiming Price $20,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: CORTE SUPREMA pressed pace, led, drew off. MIWA set pace, second best. REINA BRAVA pressed pace, weakened. CRUCERO DE AMOR trailed.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 2 7F Dirt CR: 95. Allowance Purse 14406. FOR THREE YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 117 lbs.; Older, 123 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since November 30 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since November 15 Allowed 3 lbs. A Race Since October 15 Allowed 5 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: PARTICULAR pressed pace, led, prevailed. LASTCHANCEATGLORY led, dueled, gamely. GLASS BEACH late gain inside. GREAT AZABACHE set pace, gave way. RISK VS REWARD close up, wide turn, weakened.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 3 7F Dirt CR: 69. Maiden Claiming Purse 6000. FOR MAIDENS, THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 119 lbs.; Older, 122 lbs. 4# A clasf.$4,000 y debts Allowed 4 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: POWER OF NATURE pressed pace, led, drew off. KEVIN PERFORMANCE second best. CRYPTO MINING vied for lead, weakened. ROGATIVE pressed pace, weakened. DONTONIO vied for lead, dropped back. BROTHER'S FOR LIFE dropped back. EL BUFFALO trailed.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 4 6F Dirt CR: 20. Maiden Claiming Purse 6000. FOR NATIVE MAIDENS, FILLIES AND MARES THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 117 lbs.; Older, 120 lbs. 2# A clasf.$4,000 y debts Allowed 2 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: SEFA'S SPIRIT led throughout. AMAYA BESITO outside, second best. LA NENA DEL SURI chased, even finish. CARMENCITA inside, weakened. LEYLA SOLITA failed to menace. MI NIETA LUIAN dropped back.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 5 5 1/2F Dirt CR: 73. Claiming Purse 6500. FOR FILLIES AND MARES THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 117 lbs.; Older, 121 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since November 30 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since November 15 Allowed 2 lbs. A Race Since October 15 Allowed 3 lbs. Claiming Price $8,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: FORGE AHEAD led, drew off. AMAIA MY LOVE off slowly, second best. RAW HONEY stalked pace, tired. AMAZING TRIP weakened. PROMINENCIA stalked pace, weakened. CONCEPTUS failed to menace. GEM CAT close up, weakened. STRIKE JAK dropped back. QUEEN LEDOUX very slow start. LADY RUNNER vied for lead, dropped back.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 6 5 1/2F Dirt CR: 70. Claiming Purse 6000. FOR THREE YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NOT WON A RACE SINCE JUNE 15 AND WHICH HAVE STARTED FOR A CLAIMING PRICE OF $8,000 OR LESS. Three Year Olds, 117 lbs.; Older, 121 lbs. 3# A clasf.$4,000 y debts Allowed 3 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: KID BLUE came again, driving. BLACK MAKUMBA bid outisde, led, outgamed. PAPIS INTUITION good effort. MY RUNNER RUNNER improved position. TIME OF PEACE middle of pack, evenly. NEW ACCOUNT pressed pace, dropped back. VIOLENT FIGHT failed to menace. IL PIRATA failed to menace. POKERIST dropped back.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 7 6F Dirt CR: 21. Maiden Claiming Purse 11000. FOR NATIVE MAIDENS, FILLIES TWO YEARS OLD. Weight, 116 lbs. Claiming Price $20,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: REINA KAMILA rallied, led, prevailed. FIESTA BRAVA vied for lead, led, second best. WHAT ABOUT PRINCES outside, bothered rival. DULCE PRIMAVERA vied for lead, gave way. REINA DORADA between horses, bothered stretch. RADIANCE GOLD weakened. LACHICADELAFINCA off slowly, no menace. ARABIAN MYSTIC off slowly, no menace.
